rbWSj1KojedsRJ0CmXaakvY6OXRZgdqB1oLGhxeOWAJ2X%2bg/ClD2UbAOKJFL1eHwTe3qf0zC1rXGspFct0jnefaHkMRmH1uCkLU1ihsAOw74yU3U7UGc%2bhJGI8uCqQeUBB0v4GtBpBbvh5MPdCAXDTXZUtD1BvOPGL0R3JtHON3A8zOaK7DFAc0UIec8UIvmu9MdtyQ4xjTyc1UMA5jdz0M/XCmjUkVy/dmET6uPAql29O9%2blLsrr%2bZP0BM9weQFwVViMYP6Y6B6VGkcYS5/0Y83fNTFpXgHF4DIi1F31Hz%2bwlwa/ri%2blL5Kv8fAIMKL8Dms7%2bSrfI/svLCUP/Qo4Gt3RKmTJa7F9pqQJYI2nKmLmUbOySNzo8G9T8N%2bGnAMr//AkeBozXYcIMUAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"484\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/6-1.21c3eac.4ce6eb58e9bb4836c698425963179b1e.png 484w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 484px) 100vw, 484px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/6-1.21c3eac.4ce6eb58e9bb4836c698425963179b1e.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/6-1.21c3eac.4ce6eb58e9bb4836c698425963179b1e.png\" width=\"484\"></noscript></p>\n<h2 id=\"use-cases\"><a href=\"#use-cases\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Use Cases</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>OKR and KPI Tracking System  </li>\n<li>Automated Goal Management Agent  </li>\n<li>Performance Evaluation and Optimization System  </li>\n<li>AI Agent Self-Evaluation System  </li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"implementation-cases\"><a href=\"#implementation-cases\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Implementation Cases</h2>\n<h3 id=\"customer-support-automation\"><a href=\"#customer-support-automation\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Customer Support Automation</h3>\n<p>The agent's goal is <strong>“to resolve customer fee inquiries”</strong><br>\nMonitor the conversation, check database items, and adjust fees using tools.<br>\nSuccess is monitored by checking for fee changes and receiving positive customer feedback.<br>\nIf the problem is not resolved, escalate to the supervisor.</p>\n<h3 id=\"personalized-learning-system\"><a href=\"#personalized-learning-system\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Personalized Learning System</h3>\n<p>The learning agent's goal is <strong>“to improve students' understanding of algebra”</strong><br>\nMonitor the progress of students on practice problems, adjust learning materials, track performance indicators such as accuracy and completion time, and modify the approach if the learner is struggling.\nTrack performance indicators such as accuracy and completion time, and modify the approach if the learner is struggling.</p>\n<h3 id=\"project-management-assistant\"><a href=\"#project-management-assistant\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Project Management Assistant</h3>\n<p>The agent is responsible for <strong>“ensuring project milestone X is completed by the date”</strong><br>\nMonitor the status of work, team communication, and resource availability, and notify the supervisor if the goal is at risk, and propose corrective actions.</p>\n<h3 id=\"automated-trading-bot\"><a href=\"#automated-trading-bot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Automated Trading Bot</h3>\n<p>The trading agent's goal is <strong>“to maximize portfolio returns within the risk tolerance range”</strong><br>\nMonitor market data, current portfolio value, risk indicators, and adjust the strategy when the condition matches the goal and the risk threshold is violated.\nWhen the condition matches the goal and the risk threshold is violated, execute the trade and adjust the strategy.</p>\n<h3 id=\"robotics-and-autonomous-driving-car\"><a href=\"#robotics-and-autonomous-driving-car\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Robotics and Autonomous Driving Car</h3>\n<p>The main goal of the autonomous driving car is <strong>“to safely transport the vehicle from A to B”</strong><br>\nMonitor the environment (other vehicles, pedestrians, traffic signals, road signals, speed, fuel, planned route, etc.), and adjust the driving behavior to efficiently achieve the goal.</p>\n<h3 id=\"content-moderation\"><a href=\"#content-moderation\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Content Moderation</h3>\n<p>The agent's goal is <strong>“to identify and remove inappropriate content from platform X”</strong><br>\nMonitor the incoming content, track indicators such as offensive speech, typos/missing letters, and adjust the filtering criteria or escalate cases to the review team.</p>\n<hr>\n","sidebar":"getting-started","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"6. Goal Setting and Monitoring","anchor":"#6-goal-setting-and-monitoring"},{"depth":2,"value":"Definition","anchor":"#definition"},{"depth":2,"value":"Key Features","anchor":"#key-features"},{"depth":2,"value":"Goal Monitoring Cycle","anchor":"#goal-monitoring-cycle"},{"depth":2,"value":"Use Cases","anchor":"#use-cases"},{"depth":2,"value":"Implementation Cases","anchor":"#implementation-cases"},{"depth":3,"value":"Customer Support Automation","anchor":"#customer-support-automation"},{"depth":3,"value":"Personalized Learning System","anchor":"#personalized-learning-system"},{"depth":3,"value":"Project Management Assistant","anchor":"#project-management-assistant"},{"depth":3,"value":"Automated Trading Bot","anchor":"#automated-trading-bot"},{"depth":3,"value":"Robotics and Autonomous Driving Car","anchor":"#robotics-and-autonomous-driving-car"},{"depth":3,"value":"Content Moderation","anchor":"#content-moderation"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/zh/getting-started/process-gpt-install/","title":"Process-GPT 安装指南"}},{"node":{"path":"/zh/getting-started/","title":"开始使用 Process-GPT"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv5/","title":"멀티플 인스턴스로 실행하는 고객 맞춤 뉴스레터 프로세스"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv4/","title":"ERP 데이터 연동을 통한 재고 관리"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv3/","title":"조건 분기 설정과 피드백 반영"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv2/","title":"AI 에이전트를 활용한 제안서 작성"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/tutorial/tutorial-lv1/","title":"프로세스 생성과 실행"}},{"node":{"path":"/ko/design-pattern/tool-use/"